{
  "stem": "3002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she didn't let him go to the Hitler Jugend that all the young people had to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for that, she was punished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They sent him to the Russian front, her son.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she kept him-- she always used to tell me, Janina, you just don't look like a maid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that I heard very often.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every time I heard it, I got very, very scared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Every time the bell rang in the evening, I thought, here they come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there two years going Sunday sometimes to this Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was even a Pole that wanted to marry me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I could have had it easier, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I was there till after near two years [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there came an order that no German can employ a foreigner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed people in the factories very badly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's how they sent me to this labor camp in Kremmen, which--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a Pole, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two hours, maybe, by train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I arrived to this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They put me in a room with other Polish girls-- one room, over 30 of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were all kinds of those girls, because they used to take them from street, send them to the factories in Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you could find there from the very educated to the lowest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little stove with one burner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were always fighting going on, who's going to cook the potatoes first.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
